title: The walls could finally be closing in on Donald Trump
punchline: Trump faces multiple legal challenges and a divided Republican Party
summary: Former President Donald Trump is facing multiple legal challenges and a divided Republican Party, raising questions about his political future. Trump is under investigation by the Justice Department for his role in the January 6 Capitol riot, and he is also facing a number of civil lawsuits. In addition, Trump is facing a primary challenge from Florida Governor Ron DeSantis, who is seen as a potential successor to Trump in the Republican Party.
author: MSN
